  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you choose this Inquiry at 3rd Level, you gain Mastery in Hackers and Forgery Toolkits.</p><p>These Toolkits gain additional charges equal to your Intelligence modifier.</p><p>When you would spend a charge of your Hackers Kit and succeed hacking into a system, you can spend 5 CCD Chakra.</p><p>If you do, you can cast Beast Sense on the target as if it were an animal.</p><p>Any cameras in the system become your eyes, any microphones become your ears.</p><p></p>",
